AMERICAN CHAMPAGNES

America can now be proud of the dry sparkling wines produced within its borders. Only a decade ago, one would not have thought it was possible to achieve the balance, finesse, and true excellence that is demonstrated by the superior Champagnes produced at the Korbel Vineyards and Schramsberg Vineyards of California. Both of these can hold their heads high even in the noblest company of French Champagnes. We recommend them unreservedly.
